excerpt.rendered:
A nice hoodie of good quality with the Alumax logo embroidered on the upper arm.

Color: Navy blue
Embroidery color: Orange
Composition: 100% polyester
Washing instructions: 30 degrees washable
Finishing: inside roughened
Product certification: Vegan, Fair Working Conditions, Reach Conform.

Available in sizes M, L and XL.
